headline: New research shows top OEMs cut downtime recovery by 40%, strengthening profitability through resilience-first strategies
summary: Rockwell Automation (NYSE: ROK), the world's largest company dedicated to industrial automation and digital transformation, today released new global research that highlights how leading machine builders are strengthening performance, resilience and customer trust amid increasingly complex operating conditions.
